128
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:46,220
Zhiyuan

129
00:06:46,710 --> 00:06:49,660
doesn't like Zhao Xuanxue.

130
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,370
It was all part of my plan.

131
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:55,000
You don't even know

132
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:55,930
who Zhiyuan likes.

133
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,640
So you really are

134
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,050
blind to the truth.

135
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,220
Oh, my leader.

136
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:11,970
You dedicated your entire life
to Zhao Xuanxue.

137
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,540
But in the end,

138
00:07:13,670 --> 00:07:15,780
it was all in vain.

139
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:19,140
