to turn things around.

140
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,730
Listen to my advice.

141
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,260
End it yourself.

142
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,720
Otherwise,

143
00:07:25,710 --> 00:07:27,170
