144
00:07:35,230 --> 00:07:36,220
Do you think

145
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:38,640
I should kill someone

146
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,580
as blind as him?

147
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,260
You killed Zhao Xuanxue

148
