164
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,090
Emotions?

165
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:24,090
What use are they?

166
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:27,500
You said my father loves me.

167
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,240
But since I was young,

168
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,660
I was never well-fed or warmly clothed.

169
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:32,690
To survive,

170
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,860
I joined the troupe at a young age.

171
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:37,050
To practice my skills,

172
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:40,210
I endured countless beatings.

173
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,410
Chen Shouting was my teacher.

174
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,000
But he never

175
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,290
liked me.

176
00:08:45,430 --> 00:08:46,270
It was as if

177
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:47,380
my existence

178
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:50,050
