his beloved Zhao Xuanxue.

179
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:51,270
Tell me.

180
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,570
What else could I do?

181
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:56,140
Did I want it to be this way?

182
00:08:56,950 --> 00:08:58,620
I could only rely on myself

183
