184
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,080
Xiaohe.

185
00:09:09,310 --> 00:09:10,290
Zhiyuan.

186
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,860
And you.

187
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,960
I understand you.

188
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,810
We've been together for so long.

189
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,740
I have no regrets.

190
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,620
Zhiyuan.

191
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,860
