193
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:34,510
Then,

194
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:36,900
would you be willing

195
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:41,210
to perform The Peony Pavilion with me?

196
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,260
I have been waiting for this moment

197
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,050
for too long.

198
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,260
Liu Mengmei

199
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,210
