206
00:10:15,950 --> 00:10:18,980
this scene from The Peony Pavilion?

207
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,570
Is that okay?

208
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,810
Sis.

209
00:10:27,070 --> 00:10:30,090
Since you are well-versed
in poetry and literature,

210
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:34,330
