213
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:54,330
Why did he come here?

214
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,450
Father.

215
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:06,210
I also want that rattle drum.

216
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:10,510
Xiaohe, be good.

217
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,210
I'll buy it for you later.

218
00:11:13,070 --> 00:11:14,620
You always say that,

219
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,330
