224
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:30,720
Give it to me.

225
00:11:31,070 --> 00:11:32,290
Give it to me.

226
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,140
Filthy beggar,

227
00:11:36,950 --> 00:11:38,290
give it to me.

228
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:40,290
You still won't give it to me?

229
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:45,900
You pushed me?

230
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:48,270
Father.

231
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:50,290
