236
00:11:57,430 --> 00:11:58,980
He is from an opera troupe.

237
00:11:59,190 --> 00:12:00,860
I have made an arrangement with him.

238
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,930
I will be his apprentice

239
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:05,140
and follow him from now on.

240
00:12:07,550 --> 00:12:09,090
Father, don't worry.

241
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,210
I have thought it all through for you.

242
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:14,210
Once I get a foothold
in the opera troupe,

243
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,270
you can find a reason to come over.

244
00:12:16,270 --> 00:12:18,740
This way, we can be together.

245
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:59,690
My daughter!

246
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:04,980
Xiaohe.

247
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:07,110
Xiaohe.

248
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:32,410
My daughter.

249
00:13:47,190 --> 00:13:48,030
Take him away.

250
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:48,990
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

251
00:13:55,190 --> 00:13:56,030
Should the poor

252
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,500
be bullied?

253
00:14:02,310 --> 00:14:03,150
Should we kill

254
00:14:04,240 --> 00:14:05,570
because of grievances?

255
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,680
- Go.
- Go.

256
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:15,140
(Mantangchun Theater)

257
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:16,190
They are all dead.

258
