280
00:14:53,270 --> 00:14:54,950
Now that the case is closed,

281
00:14:54,950 --> 00:14:56,310
let's go to Jushangfang for a good meal.

282
00:14:56,310 --> 00:14:57,150
My treat.

283
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,080
Okay.

284
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,200
Miss,

285
00:15:07,310 --> 00:15:09,000
