to get the case result.

286
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,000
Just tell my father

287
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,990
that the case is closed and the culprit
has been identified.

288
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,160
We will write a report

289
00:15:13,160 --> 00:15:14,280
to Director Xu

290
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,120
after we go back.

